    <abstract>
      <t>In some use cases, e.g., Lightweight 4over6, the client may require not just one port, but a port set.  This document defines an extension to the Port Control Protocol (PCP) that allows clients to manipulate a set of ports as a whole.  This is accomplished using a new MAP option: PORT_SET.
	 </t>
